    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 4vw, 1.25rem); font-weight: 700; color: #151515; line-height: 1.3;">The Scale of Systemic Risk</h3>
    
    <p style="font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 3vw, 1rem); line-height: 1.6; color: #24292F; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        When a fintech has 10 users, risk is negligible. When it has 2 million, the complexity is systemic. <strong>Drag the slider</strong> to see why an 80-person company requires 11 Vice Presidents to survive.
    </p>

